::DarkMouse::

She ran into the lab and slammed the door shut.  She didn't care 
anymore. She looked around the lab.  She saw the box sitting on the 
counter.  It was the one that Scorponok had told her not to touch. 
She was so mad and hurt by him she didn't care at all about 
anything.  She walked over to the box, picked it up and looked at 
it.  She felt a tear run down her face.  She raised the box up over 
her head and threw as hard as she could onto the floor.  It broke 
into a million pieces.  When it broke, she fell to the floor in 
stasis lock, with her memory erased.
